name: 16 Memory Card - Eff The Alien
description: An alien figure who has the ability to mimic and blend in the hustle and bustle of the Andalusian district. While on the Earth, he borrowed a man's form in strange and quite flashy clothes then observed the habit and the emotions of Earth's creatures. Actually, his main task of him is to be the messenger to his followers (the alien adherent group, Aeon) A microchip that was written completely stated that Lucid City would become one of the first alien colonies and established a new imperial city under the rule of Mars.
